<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-03-14T09:20:15-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-03-14T09:20:15-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-14T09:20:15-04:00</updated><title> SpaceX 星舰发射：第三次有魅力吗？</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;发射台上的星舰测试飞行器，前景有 SpaceX 标志&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/_y36KoFKhJKlou5234DAYHsImE8=/338x0:3502x2109/1310x873/cdn. vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73206353/GIfp_2Ya0AAHUJF.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：&lt;a class=&quot;ql-link&quot; href=&quot;https://twitter.com/SpaceX/status /1767638654334468523&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;SpaceX&lt;/a>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;前两次星舰飞行测试以爆炸性方式结束。现在，SpaceX 已经确定了第三次发射尝试的日期和时间。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24100089/spacex-starship-launch-date-time-flight -test-三&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24100089/spacex-starship-launch-date-time-flight-test-three" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24100089/spacex-starship-launch-date-time-flight-test- Three</id><author><name>理查德·劳勒</name><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name><name>阿姆丽塔·哈立德</name><name>乔治娜·托贝特</name><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name><name>艾玛·罗斯</name><name>洛伦·格鲁什</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-03-14T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-14T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>迷你但功能强大：Blink 的小型廉价相机现在可以在户外使用</title><content type="html">&lt;p>;新款 Blink Mini 2 有线安全摄像头是 Blink Mini 的值得升级，增加了耐候性、更宽的视野和人员检测功能，价格约为 40 美元。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/24100149/blink-mini-2-review&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24100149/blink-mini-2-review" rel="alterna